data.description: Bring your fishing poles and come enjoy all that highly sought after Annslee Lakes has to offer! This 3/2.5 has new paint, new stove, newly remodeled bathrooms with walk-in tile shower and secondary bathroom. Also enjoy a bonus room that could be a home office, playroom or anything you can dream of! Home has Nest thermostat, alarm and door bell with Hue lightbulbs making this beautiful home a smart home that can be controlled from your phone, Alexa and Google.  Oversized master suite has two separate walk-in closets. Kitchen has tons of cabinet space and overlooks large family room. Home contains huge fenced in private backyard with covered and screened back patio. Situated on a beautiful corner lot. Sharon elementary and Loganville Middle/High schools.
